Package: brody
Version: 1.0.0
Section: interpreters
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6
Installed-Size: 80
Maintainer: Brody nnov.brody@gmail.com
Description: Brody programming language interpreter
 Brody is a lightweight scripting language inspired by Python, Lua and Bash.
 Supports variables, functions, lists, control flow, shell commands and imports.
 File extension: .br
